			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This AD plays during the Ketheric Showdown in the lower Colony. It will play on Nightsong.\r\n\r\n- Load SCL_Main_A\r\n- Using ReCon command \"oe KethericShowdown_Start\"  to teleport yourself there.\r\n- Use \"oe KethericShowdown_Transform\". This will initiate stage 2 and transform Ketheric into the Apostle of Myrkul.\r\n- Once Nightsong gets her first turn in combat (and she is available to speak), this AD will play on her."
				},
